            streaming data from internal data sources and 3rd party systems like SalesForce.

      .col-md-6.m-b-3
        .row
          .col-md-3.col-xs-12.text-md-right.text-xs-center
            %img{ src: "assets/images/icons/machine-learning.png", class:"icon m-b-1" }
