            specific points of interest is simple and fast.


      .col-md-6.m-b-3
        .row
          .col-md-3.col-xs-12.text-md-right.text-xs-center
            %img{ src: "assets/images/icons/collab.png", class:"icon m-b-1" }
          .col-md-9.text-md-left.text-xs-center
